            "body": "I don't think it's the same bug. Proposed workaround in that one has no effect on my issue. But the description that it's obscured by cursor shifting seems to match, because I'm using a setting that prevents cursor from moving back when exiting insert mode:\r\n```\r\n\" preventing cursor shifting when exiting insert mode\r\nau InsertLeave * :normal `^\r\n```",
